<br>
-5stam = less HP.  Less HP = not as good at takin a hit.<br>
<br>
its a nice rogue weapon, or a ranger weapon, but not a warrior weapon.  Its speed makes it too slow for aggro, its ratio makes it good for DPS, no proc means it wont draw additional aggro, and the neg5 stam makes it even worse, as it takes 25hp from you at lvl50 (5points per stam at 50).<br>
<br>
If i were your wife, id put Bloodfire in offhand (or sell it alltogether), Pick up a frostbringer for mainhand. It will be the best weapon you ever buy, nothing comes close to the pound for pound value of a frostbringer.  And like Brutal said, save for a fleshgrinder, or a Swiftblade, or Shortblade. <p>Veteran Smakz Mabytchup<br>
